quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  26,160,Abantu b’intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) nabone barahakanye intumwa z’Imana
  26,161,"Mugihe yababwira mwene wabo na Lutwi (iii) ati:- mbega mwebwe ntimutinya Imana yanyu"
  26,162,Mu vy’ukuri jewe kuri mwebwe nd’intumwa y’Imana yizigiwe
  26,163,"Rero ni mutinye Imana yanyu, nanje mu ngamburukire"
  26,164,"Kandi jewe sindabasaba impembo kuri ibi vyose, mugabo impembo yanje iri kumana w’ibiremwa vyose"
  26,165,Mbega mwebwe murangura amabanga yabubatse n’abagabo nkamwe mubiremwa vy’imana
  26,166,"Mukareka\tabo\tUmuremyi\twanyu\tyabaremeye\tmubagore\tbanyu,\tmu vy’ukuri mwebwe muri mubantu mwarenze uburimbi"
  26,167,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- nutareka kutubuza wewe Lutwi (iii) ntankeka wewe uzoba uri mubantu bazokwirukanwa ngaha muri iki gisagara turimwo"
  26,168,"Nawe abishura ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe ndimu bantu banka cane ivyo bikorwa vyanyu bigaritse vy’umwanda"
  26,169,Muremyi wanje nundokore n’aba bantu banje kuri ibi bintu bariko baragira
  26,170,Natwe duca turamurokora n’abantu biwe bose
  26,171,Dukuyemwo umutamakazi yari mubicara inyuma y’abandi bose
  26,172,Hanyuma duca turabahonya b’abandi
  26,173,"Duca tubamanurira imvura y’isegenya mbi cane, nayo yari iyaba gabishijwe"
  26,174,"Ntankeka ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo, mugabo benshi muribo ntibari mubantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  26,175,Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe nyene ububasha n’impuhwe zihagije